.DS_Store

# Rust build output (rust/wasm-bridge, rust/tools/*, rust/vendor/*) — these get
# huge (multi-GB with -Z build-std) and are always reproducible from source.
target/

# Vendored, patched dependencies (anki @ 985MB, systemstat, burn-train) —
# reproducible via rust/vendor-patches/regen.sh (pristine upstream source +
# the .patch files there, which ARE tracked). See docs/ARCHITECTURE.md §6/§10.
rust/vendor/
